snippet.title: Pulzar - Amstrad CPC Homebrew
snippet.description:
One of the more recent CPC homebrew games, you have to evade solar storms to escape galactic police.

Developed by Snaut
Also released for ZX Spectrum
Download: https://snauts.itch.io/pulzar
